This creates a sophisticated color-picker web component with:
Core Features:
HSV Color Selection: Interactive saturation/value box with hue slider
Multiple Input Modes: HEX, RGB, HSL with real-time conversion
Opacity Control: Optional alpha channel with checkerboard background
Native Eyedropper: Screen color picking using EyeDropper API (Chrome 95+)
Theme Integration:
Sharingan Presets: Tomoe Red, Sharingan Black, Iris Crimson, Chakra Blue
Mangekyō Presets: Mangekyo Red, Amaterasu Black, Tsukuyomi Purple, Susanoo Blue
EMS Presets: Eternal Crimson, Rinnegan Purple, Limbo Gray, God Tree
Visual Effects: Pulsing animations for theme colors, glow effects
User Experience:
Color History: Automatically saves last 8 picked colors to localStorage
Custom Presets: Save user-defined colors with custom names
Keyboard Navigation: Full accessibility support
Smart Positioning: Popup with collision detection
Smooth Animations: Transitions on all interactive elements
Technical Implementation:
Color Math: Full HSL↔RGB↔HEX conversion utilities
Drag Support: Smooth dragging on all sliders with pointer events
Debounced Updates: Performance-optimized input handling
Shadow DOM: Full encapsulation with CSS custom properties for theming

Usage Example:

<color-picker 
  value="#ff4757" 
  theme-preset="sharingan"
  show-opacity
  show-eyedropper
  allow-custom-presets
  label="Accent Color">
</color-picker>